    "updated_at": "2025-02-12T17:05:20Z",
    "body": "This is pretty easy to do with a custom section:\n\n```toml\nformat ='''\n$character\\\n${custom.spcr}\\\n$os\\\n${custom.spcr}\\\n$username\\\n$directory\\\n${custom.spcr}\\\n$git-branch\\\n'''\n\n[custom.spcr]\nwhen = true\nformat = \"[ | ]($style)\"\nstyle = \"fg:prev_fg bg:prev_bg\"\n```",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
