    "created_at": "2025-07-14T18:49:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-07-14T18:50:00Z",
    "body": "In my case this is what I currently use. It's doing the job\n\n```\n[docker_context]\nsymbol = \" \"\nstyle  = \"bold blue\"\nformat = '| [$symbol$context]($style) '\nonly_with_files = false\n\n[kubernetes]\nsymbol = \"☸ \"\nformat = '| [$symbol$context( \\($namespace\\))]($style) '\nstyle  = \"cyan bold\"\ndisabled = false\n\n[helm]\nsymbol = \"󰠳 \"\nstyle  = \"bold purple\"\nformat = '| [$symbol]($style) '\n\n[terraform]\nsymbol = \"󱁢 \"\nstyle = \"bold 105\"\ndetect_extensions = [\"hcl\", \"tf\"]\ndetect_files      = [\"terragrunt.hcl\"]\ndetect_folders    = [\".terraform\", \".terragrunt-cache\"]\nformat = '| [$symbol$workspace]($style) '\n...\n...\n...\n...\n```\n\nAs you can see, adding the | at the beginning in the format section will added it at the beginning. \n\n<img width=\"712\" height=\"106\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8f83ec96-1889-46e9-9a84-e9e532e7343b\" />",
